<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Oct 2021 07:01:56 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>GTA 三部曲重製版     PC、Switch、PS、手機多平台</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/DtXB_T2VJHk/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 11 Oct 2021 07:01:41 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy – The Definitive Edition]]></category><category><![CDATA[gta]]></category><category><![CDATA[GTA:III]]></category><category><![CDATA[GTA:San Andreas]]></category><category><![CDATA[GTA:Vice City]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1064907</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Rockstar Games 日前證實將開發數款 Grand Theft Auto（GTA）系列游戲重製版，包 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Rockstar Games 日前證實將開發數款 Grand Theft Auto（GTA）系列游戲重製版，包括 GTA:III、GTA:Vice City 以及 GTA:San Andreas。有消息指，該款遊戲將在電腦、Xbox、PlayStation 及任天堂 Switch 上率先發佈，2022 上半年亦將會推出 iOS 及 Android 推出，但確切的發佈日期及價錢則有待官方確認公佈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1064908" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5BDC01FA-B974-441B-9667-5329AA7898B0-694x416.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5BDC01FA-B974-441B-9667-5329AA7898B0-694x416.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5BDC01FA-B974-441B-9667-5329AA7898B0-768x461.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/5BDC01FA-B974-441B-9667-5329AA7898B0.jpeg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據了解，以上提及的三款經典遊戲（GTA:III、GTA:Vice City 以及 GTA:San Andreas）重製版將不會單獨售賣，而是以套裝《Grand Theft Auto: The Trilogy – The Definitive Edition》形式發售。到目前為止，Rockstar Games 尚未有公佈重製作版將會進行哪方面的提升或重置，但有透露將會對遊戲畫質進行提升以及遊戲內容上的現代化升級。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1064909" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/32AE719F-8629-4C43-B8B9-D00B0F43D2E8.png" alt="" width="550" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/32AE719F-8629-4C43-B8B9-D00B0F43D2E8.png 550w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/32AE719F-8629-4C43-B8B9-D00B0F43D2E8-120x120.png 120w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 550px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Rockstar Games 表示，重製版應將在近期發佈，但發佈前將重電商平台移除現時的原版 GTA 遊戲。若有玩家希望保留或鍾情於原版遊戲就需要盡快購買了，否則將從平台上永遠無法購得原版遊戲。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://venturebeat.com/2021/10/08/grand-theft-auto-trilogy-remake-coming-to-modern-consoles-and-pc/">VentureBeat</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
